data.name: textInputReplaceBy.ToolTip
data.value: Replacement substring to use in the package's internal resource names (TXTRs, TXMTs, XTOLs and GZPSs). It should only contain letters, numbers, dashes and underscores. An empty string erases what it substitutes.

data.name: textInputToReplace.ToolTip
data.value: Substring to find and replace in the package's internal resource names (TXTRs, TXMTs, XTOLs and GZPSs). It should only contain letters, numbers, dashes and underscores. Not substitution is done when this string is empty.
